commit.message: use the README for the long description
Without xlsx, we have no opportunity for xml vulnerabilities.
Installation of python packages is standardised now.
Give sensible exceptions when we know we can't open a file.
Add helper to figure out what type of file you have.
remove unused code and exclude debug branches from coverage checks
move all the samples to their own folder
strip out xlsx code, tests and samples
Move the change log to the root.
